{"tid":1700532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不割席不分化 係咪代表做乜都唔割","createTime":"2019-11-08T14:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T16:24:53.000Z","uid":58555,"like":9,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"fc58859390db27adf5f4601c5daf2856eb0a265a","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"可能講得唔啱聽 歡迎屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設運動已經進化到破壞所有政府基建<br />\n圖書館、康文署、博物館等等<br />\n如果要濫殺無辜、破壞歷史文物<br />\n多口都要問一句 割唔割?<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過不割席可以成為對家侮辱示威者聲譽嘅武器<br />\n我嘅意思唔係話見到手足有新行動就割<br />\n但係係咪行動後應該保留理性嘅討論空間<br />\n而唔係一尾盲撐盲攬有可能係被仇恨沖昏嘅手足呢<br />\n<br />\n運動已經第五個月 行動上 思想上都要有進化<br />\n積極討論同檢討 先係上上策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</strong></span>－ 梁天琦"},{"pid":"b3dc000b5e927e3948b13b4038642d09f50550b2","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"890908c72cb46aa9831457348335753f83e10f02","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dfe68200d83b34c74ce7fda5975f284d4642dc0e","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85daef9ca9b0e1b079ed5f6e4e57cc5d1a9d61c2","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d78d570a5e2600661b118b166188cf7e02e52349","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e360c347120869a1eb9bef49dc28e3560afacde3","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"947e2fd5f8bd630e6edf541f87938f17f904c53b","tid":1700