\n博物館如果完全唔講中共黑暗嘅歷史 讚美中國偉大 奶到共產黨雪雪聲 咁燒佢都係無錯<br />\n<br />\n咁樣叫盲撐咩？ 咁樣叫走火入魔咩 到底邊個先係走火入魔呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"問題係好撚多人未知行動方向同結果已經嗌定不割席 做嗰個係咪手足都未知 咁快就當人係手足"},{"pid":"963906c4a191e9ce1d296482475b3afa525c5b4f","tid":1700532,"uid":261699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"呢一刻即使前線手足只係為宣洩憤怒而&quot;做錯&quot;任何事<br />\n都無必要割"},{"pid":"2e785ccbcbdef7c91c07c68e025896b848a7e1dd","tid":1700532,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"可以改善 但做咗都唔割"},{"pid":"edfe4bedf4e336289ccda53f331fee94c476c033","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9eadcd20950264229bc48b797fe9092e4ca864","tid":1700532,"uid":291525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警甴死撚晒都唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"屌你 唔撚係講殺警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺警同殺保皇黨我十萬個同意 !"},{"pid":"acba5af94c07dfdd2f7cbc8089085de704fd84dd","tid":1700532,"uid":72879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08d32a702ec883e08f4d6deebf8eb95981c00908","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f647215875866fe7bb0253ca4e8f7cac14a53524","tid":1700532,"uid":72879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc58859390db27adf5f4601c5daf2856eb0a265a","tid":1700532,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"可能講得唔啱聽 歡迎屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設運動已經進化到破壞所有政府基建<br />\n圖書館、康文署、博物館等等<br />\n如果要濫殺無辜、破壞歷史文物<br />\n多口都要問一句 割唔割?<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過不割席可以成為對